LOG DATE: [ERROR - DATA CORRUPT]


We have constructed this bunker as precaution against whatever ills might befall us in this new realm.

Granted, there are few obvious threats here - the wild animals are largely peaceable, and the undead are, while unusual, only a threat to the stupid and the unwary.

A few have brought up the possiblity of the natives - Phenuans as we have taken to calling them - being a danger, but those concerns have been largely waved off as improbable.

While they have developed some novel essentimagical applications, they are rather primative and of little threat to even a moderately well-equipped Researcher.


- Second-class Architech-Researcher Kazari Bulok

The local Phenuans have risen up, attacking our factories and research centers.

Though I am confident that our automated weapons platforms and defensive drones are more than capable of handling them, a hiearched team of ten Researchers - lead by myself, the 11th - have retreated to this bunker as a provisionary measure, in the unlikely event of the Phenuans somehow gaining the upper hand.


- Head Essence-Researcher Ekkari Bulok
